text: Rawhide is a 1951 American western movie directed by Henry Hathaway and starring Tyrone Power, Susan Hayward, Dean Jagger, Hugh Marlowe, George Tobias, Jack Elam, Edgar Buchanan. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1951 movies Category:1950s Western (genre) movies Category:American Western (genre) movies Category:Movies directed by Henry Hathaway
